一直到 3 月底通知了其他人唯独没通知我去报到，我三番五次打电话去问才知道举报的事情 ，并且没有启动任何调查程序。现在弄得我处于失业状态，社保医保都断交了， 我该怎么通过合法有效的途径维护自身权益？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-22f98986c45ce312a39a0fb38b477949_1440w.jpg?source=172ae18b"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "503 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/452842138"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IgfbgqvPO+Zs7EAMaCDYyOTExMjM3IM+DpYMGMAY43ARAD3IJNDUyODQyMTM4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1618834480.667969", "card_id": "Q_443701759", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 53}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "4000 个狗狗币，值得长期持有吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "就一直放着，放它五年后回来看下这个问题。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-ee0d7a1a406ab8281ebc791ea713f996_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "438 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/443701759"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IgfbgqvPO+Zs7EAMaCDYwODc4NzU3IITfioEGMAA4qgFAEHIJNDQzNzAxNzU5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1618834480.6684144", "card_id": "Q_455166469", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 207}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "三星回应一男子手机在包中爆炸被烧伤，到底发生了什么？如何看待三星手机的又一次爆炸事件？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "4 月 15 日，河南郑州，有网友爆料，一名男子和朋友走在路上时包里的三星手机突然爆炸，背包瞬间起火。皮肤被烧伤，头发和睫毛等被烧焦。据悉该手机为三星 G5700。 三星回应：若有用户反映该情况，将有专人联系用户本人予以处理。其他内容暂时不便透露。到底发生了什么？ （视频来自沸点视频）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-6981483f67877c6b4a1edbbcde275a2d_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "433 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/455166469"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IgfbgqvPO+Zs7EAMaCDYzNDI3ODQ5IJnW64MGMCA4lwZAEXIJNDU1MTY2NDY5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "sty